1375
01:36:30,159 --> 01:36:31,279
[SPEAKER_00] Pa i ovim

1376
01:36:31,279 --> 01:36:32,899
[SPEAKER_00] društveno-političkim,

1377
01:36:32,899 --> 01:36:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] ekonomskim previranjima.

1378
01:36:36,859 --> 01:36:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] kako odgajati

1379
01:36:38,340 --> 01:36:39,680
