1380
01:36:39,680 --> 01:36:40,760
[SPEAKER_00] to je dječak.

1381
01:36:40,760 --> 01:36:43,600
[SPEAKER_01] Sadnji put si rekao da nisi bio zadovoljan

1382
01:36:43,600 --> 01:36:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] mojim odgovorom.

1383
01:36:44,380 --> 01:36:46,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam baš rekao da nisi bio zadovoljan.

1384
