1385
01:36:47,300 --> 01:36:48,060
[SPEAKER_01] Baš sam se...

1386
01:36:48,060 --> 01:36:49,520
[SPEAKER_00] gleda su politički korekt.

1387
01:36:51,520 --> 01:36:52,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ali stvarno je,

1388
01:36:52,819 --> 01:36:54,239
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek se fokusiramo,

1389
01:36:54,239 --> 01:36:55,380
[SPEAKER_01] sad sam sve ispričala,

1390
01:36:55,380 --> 01:36:57,420
[SPEAKER_01] fokusiramo se ispod sante leda.

1391
01:36:57,420 --> 01:36:59,239
[SPEAKER_01] A ispod sante leda

1392
