[SPEAKER_01] malo različitiji.

1394
01:37:01,880 --> 01:37:02,600
[SPEAKER_01] To je istina.

1395
01:37:02,600 --> 01:37:03,600
[SPEAKER_01] Naprimjer,

1396
01:37:03,600 --> 01:37:04,680
[SPEAKER_01] djevojčice će biti možda

1397
01:37:04,680 --> 01:37:05,739
