[SPEAKER_01] taj dio postoji.

1404
01:37:13,739 --> 01:37:15,399
[SPEAKER_01] I tu će onda opet,

1405
01:37:15,399 --> 01:37:17,140
[SPEAKER_01] ali mi gledamo ispod sante leda,

1406
01:37:17,140 --> 01:37:18,319
[SPEAKER_01] pa ću tom dječaku

1407
01:37:18,319 --> 01:37:20,100
[SPEAKER_01] možda morati više granica postavljati

1408
01:37:20,100 --> 01:37:21,399
[SPEAKER_01] i biti puno srpljivija.

1409
01:37:21,399 --> 01:37:24,600
[SPEAKER_01] Djevojčici ću možda više s njom pričati.

1410
01:37:24,600 --> 01:37:24,920
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1411
01:37:24,920 --> 01:37:27,260
[SPEAKER_01] u tom smislu uvijek se prilagođavam

1412
01:37:27,260 --> 01:37:29,779
[SPEAKER_01] osobi koje je ispred mene.

1413
01:37:29,779 --> 01:37:32,779
[SPEAKER_01] A što se tiče...

1414
01:37:32,779 --> 01:37:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] Koji bi bio cilje, recimo,

1415
01:37:33,960 --> 01:37:36,180
[SPEAKER_00] odgoja surici ili dječaka?

1416
01:37:36,180 --> 01:37:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] Da li vidiš

1417
01:37:37,039 --> 01:37:39,560
[SPEAKER_00] nekakve različite ovaj...

1418
01:37:39,560 --> 01:37:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo imati toliko teško pitanje.

1419
01:37:41,619 --> 01:37:42,640
[SPEAKER_01] E, ali znaš šta?

1420
01:37:42,640 --> 01:37:43,699
[SPEAKER_00] Srašno teško pitanje.

1421
01:37:43,699 --> 01:37:45,319
[SPEAKER_01] Je, ali kad bi gledala,

1422
01:37:45,319 --> 01:37:47,239
[SPEAKER_01] jer mi opet ih odgajamo za svijet

1423
01:37:47,239 --> 01:37:47,819
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem jesmo.

1424
01:37:47,819 --> 01:37:49,260
[SPEAKER_01] I sad ja razmišljam djevojčicu.

1425
01:37:49,260 --> 01:37:51,100
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, odgajala bi ju da

1426
01:37:51,100 --> 01:37:53,899
[SPEAKER_01] da ima svoje ja,

1427
01:37:53,899 --> 01:37:55,840
[SPEAKER_01] da osjeti tu svoju snagu,

1428
01:37:55,840 --> 01:37:57,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer kod nas još uvijek je.

1429
01:37:57,340 --> 01:37:59,899
[SPEAKER_01] Muškarci su ti koji su na pozicijama,

1430
01:37:59,899 --> 01:38:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] koje su više.

1431
01:38:00,840 --> 01:38:03,319
[SPEAKER_01] Gledaj ih se.

1432
01:38:03,319 --> 01:38:05,119
[SPEAKER_01] Još uvijek je o...

1433
01:38:05,119 --> 01:38:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] Još uvijek

1434
01:38:05,920 --> 01:38:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] i u strukama sličnima meni.

1435
01:38:07,380 --> 01:38:08,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ako muškarac sad sjedi

1436
