1437
01:38:09,939 --> 01:38:11,939
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi će mu vjerovat puno više

1438
01:38:11,939 --> 01:38:12,680
[SPEAKER_01] nego meni.

1439
01:38:12,680 --> 01:38:13,600
[SPEAKER_01] Bez obzira što sam ja

1440
01:38:13,600 --> 01:38:14,359
[SPEAKER_01] majka dvoje djece,

1441
01:38:14,359 --> 01:38:15,119
[SPEAKER_01] što sam ih rodila.

1442
01:38:15,119 --> 01:38:17,300
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, još uvijek je taj dio

1443
01:38:17,300 --> 01:38:18,680
[SPEAKER_01] da nam muškarci izgledaju

1444
01:38:18,680 --> 01:38:19,439
[SPEAKER_01] malo...

1445
01:38:19,439 --> 01:38:22,100
[SPEAKER_01] malo stručnije,

1446
01:38:22,100 --> 01:38:23,279
[SPEAKER_01] malo pametnije.

1447
01:38:23,279 --> 01:38:23,779
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

1448
01:38:23,779 --> 01:38:25,739
[SPEAKER_01] definitivno u tom smjeru jačat.

1449
01:38:25,739 --> 01:38:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ali,

1450
01:38:26,260 --> 01:38:29,159
[SPEAKER_01] ono što zadnji put što ljudi nisu voljeli,

1451
01:38:29,159 --> 01:38:30,939
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo zadnji put snimeli podcast,

1452
01:38:30,939 --> 01:38:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam rekla,

1453
01:38:31,539 --> 01:38:33,039
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da bi mama mogla,

1454
01:38:33,039 --> 01:38:36,060
[SPEAKER_01] morala moći biti doma,

1455
01:38:36,060 --> 01:38:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno,

1456
01:38:37,000 --> 01:38:37,720
[SPEAKER_01] ne doma,

1457
01:38:37,720 --> 01:38:39,380
[SPEAKER_01] nego raditi pola radnog vremena.

1458
01:38:40,119 --> 01:38:41,180
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je bilo kao,

1459
01:38:41,180 --> 01:38:41,560
[SPEAKER_01] a tata,

1460
01:38:41,560 --> 01:38:42,079
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1461
01:38:42,079 --> 01:38:43,699
[SPEAKER_01] ono bilo je baš napada.

1462
01:38:43,699 --> 01:38:44,840
[SPEAKER_01] Možda sam išla iz perspektive

1463
01:38:44,840 --> 01:38:45,479
[SPEAKER_01] koja je moja,

1464
01:38:45,479 --> 01:38:46,340
[SPEAKER_01] kao ja bi voljela.

1465
01:38:46,340 --> 01:38:49,439
[SPEAKER_01] I najčešće je primarni skrbnik ta mama.

1466
01:38:49,439 --> 01:38:50,479
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ta mama rodi,

1467
01:38:50,479 --> 01:38:52,119
[SPEAKER_01] ona se povezuje s djetetom

1468
01:38:52,119 --> 01:38:54,020
[SPEAKER_01] skin to skin više nego tata.

1469
01:38:54,020 --> 01:38:55,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ona najčešće doji, hrani.

1470
01:38:55,479 --> 01:38:57,560
[SPEAKER_01] Tata ide najčešće raditi nakon 5 dana.

1471
01:38:57,560 --> 01:39:00,239
[SPEAKER_01] Nekad je možda supratno,

1472
01:39:00,239 --> 01:39:01,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali najčešće je mama,

1473
01:39:01,500 --> 01:39:03,840
[SPEAKER_01] pa sam išla s tim zapravo da kao mama.

1474
01:39:03,840 --> 01:39:06,100
[SPEAKER_01] Ali generalno,

1475
01:39:09,100 --> 01:39:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] Čekaj, moram se vratiti šta sam pričala.

1476
01:39:11,039 --> 01:39:12,220
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ćete morati rezati.

1477
01:39:12,220 --> 01:39:14,359
[SPEAKER_00] Kako? Ne, nećemo ništa rezati.

1478
01:39:14,359 --> 01:39:15,520
[SPEAKER_00] Tako ovaj,

1479
01:39:15,520 --> 01:39:17,100
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom trenutku si

1480
01:39:17,100 --> 01:39:19,319
[SPEAKER_00] rekla nešto zanimljivo zapravo,

1481
01:39:19,319 --> 01:39:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] da odgajamo

1482
01:39:20,840 --> 01:39:22,399
[SPEAKER_00] curise i dečke

1483
01:39:22,399 --> 01:39:24,100
[SPEAKER_00] u odnosu na svijet

1484
01:39:24,100 --> 01:39:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] koji trenutno postoji.

1485
01:39:25,460 --> 01:39:26,279
[SPEAKER_01] Okej, hvala.

1486
01:39:26,279 --> 01:39:27,100
[SPEAKER_01] Koji trenutno je.

1487
01:39:27,100 --> 01:39:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vidiš,

1488
01:39:28,359 --> 01:39:29,819
[SPEAKER_00] sad će se upali,

1489
01:39:29,819 --> 01:39:31,220
[SPEAKER_00] to je moj filozofski dio.

1490
01:39:31,220 --> 01:39:33,399
[SPEAKER_01] Ali daj mi dozvoli da završimo.

1491
01:39:33,399 --> 01:39:34,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde, ajde, da si su sjetila.

1492
01:39:34,699 --> 01:39:35,579
[SPEAKER_00] Može, nastavi.

1493
01:39:35,579 --> 01:39:37,979
[SPEAKER_01] Tijela sam reći da se događa,

1494
01:39:38,079 --> 01:39:41,060
[SPEAKER_01] da danas kao to izravnavanje feminizam.

1495
01:39:41,060 --> 01:39:42,819
[SPEAKER_01] Da smo mi došli do toga

1496
01:39:42,819 --> 01:39:44,060
[SPEAKER_01] da i dalje, ne znam,

1497
01:39:44,060 --> 01:39:45,659
[SPEAKER_01] neka se ljudi u komentarima jave.

1498
01:39:45,659 --> 01:39:48,180
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, ja ne znam kako je kod vas,

1499
01:39:48,180 --> 01:39:50,699
[SPEAKER_01] ali kod mene je mama 500 puta u danu,

1500
01:39:50,699 --> 01:39:51,479
[SPEAKER_01] tata dva puta.

1501
01:39:51,479 --> 01:39:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] Samo nek ljud,

1502
01:39:52,260 --> 01:39:53,020
[SPEAKER_01] baš me zanima.

1503
01:39:53,020 --> 01:39:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, baš me zanima.

1504
01:39:54,000 --> 01:39:56,060
[SPEAKER_01] I tu ne možemo protiv toga.

1505
01:39:56,060 --> 01:39:56,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možemo.

1506
01:39:56,859 --> 01:39:59,239
[SPEAKER_01] Tu sad radi biologija,

1507
01:39:59,239 --> 01:39:59,819
[SPEAKER_01] bi ja rekla.

1508
01:40:00,960 --> 01:40:03,899
[SPEAKER_01] Ali smo se mi dovele do toga da mi i radimo.

1509
01:40:03,899 --> 01:40:06,680
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, radimo 8 sati, možda i 10.

1510
01:40:06,680 --> 01:40:07,520
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, radimo.

1511
01:40:07,520 --> 01:40:09,579
[SPEAKER_01] Sve radimo ko muškarci,

1512
01:40:09,579 --> 01:40:13,300
[SPEAKER_01] ali kao da malo više toga opet spadne na nas.

1513
01:40:13,739 --> 01:40:15,359
[SPEAKER_01] S druge strane, ja rodim.

1514
01:40:15,359 --> 01:40:18,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, i tatama nije lako kad rode.

1515
01:40:18,939 --> 01:40:20,159
[SPEAKER_01] Kad rode.

1516
01:40:20,159 --> 01:40:22,319
[SPEAKER_01] Nije im lako, ali hej,

1517
01:40:22,319 --> 01:40:25,899
[SPEAKER_01] šta se u našem tijelu događa nakon što rodimo?

1518
01:40:25,899 --> 01:40:29,439
[SPEAKER_01] Evo sad samo, kako ja imam neki izuzov sa trijevima,

1519
01:40:29,439 --> 01:40:31,060
[SPEAKER_01] baš gledam žene mi se javljaju

1520
01:40:31,060 --> 01:40:33,920
[SPEAKER_01] nakon poroda, nakon poroda, nakon poroda.

1521
01:40:33,920 --> 01:40:38,239
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi tu pričamo koliko tijelu uopće treba

1522
01:40:38,239 --> 01:40:42,819
[SPEAKER_01] da se to sve vrati na svoje mjesto.

1523
01:40:43,220 --> 01:40:45,479
[SPEAKER_01] da si ti psihički i fizički dobro,

1524
01:40:45,479 --> 01:40:47,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne, mi godina dana,

1525
01:40:47,579 --> 01:40:50,100
[SPEAKER_01] mi u okviru od pet dana

1526
01:40:50,100 --> 01:40:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] dajemo djeta u jaslice i krećemo raditi.

1527
01:40:52,800 --> 01:40:55,819
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, stres što radiš protiv biologije,

1528
01:40:55,819 --> 01:40:58,039
[SPEAKER_01] protiv prirode, da ga odvajaš u jaslice,

1529
01:40:58,039 --> 01:41:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] tako maleno, koje još ne može izregulirati sebe

1530
01:41:01,039 --> 01:41:02,939
[SPEAKER_01] i daješ ga u tu grupu.

1531
01:41:02,939 --> 01:41:06,840
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, i tvoje najčešće, ako nisi zbog opet trauma,

1532
01:41:06,840 --> 01:41:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] odvojen od emocija, pa ne osjetiš ništa,

1533
01:41:09,539 --> 01:41:12,859
[SPEAKER_01] ali najčešće u dubini osjetiš da to nije,

1534
01:41:12,859 --> 01:41:14,140
[SPEAKER_01] baš ispredo teško ti je,

1535
01:41:14,140 --> 01:41:16,340
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne, ti možeš doći na posao u tih pet dana.

1536
01:41:16,340 --> 01:41:19,560
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja mislim da nama treba tri mjeseca,

1537
01:41:19,560 --> 01:41:21,859
[SPEAKER_01] ma šest, da uopće se prilagodimo,

1538
01:41:21,859 --> 01:41:23,399
[SPEAKER_01] da smo djete dali tamo,

1539
01:41:23,399 --> 01:41:25,979
[SPEAKER_01] da taj stres malo da dođemo k sebi

1540
01:41:25,979 --> 01:41:27,739
[SPEAKER_01] i onda da idem raditi.

1541
01:41:27,739 --> 01:41:30,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne, to je sve u vrlo kratkom roku.

1542
01:41:30,239 --> 01:41:33,180
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, postale smo ko muškarci,

1543
01:41:33,180 --> 01:41:36,520
[SPEAKER_01] ali je ostalo ono kako smo prije bile žene.

1544
01:41:36,520 --> 01:41:37,300
[SPEAKER_01] Najčešće.

1545
01:41:37,300 --> 01:41:39,479
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, da, muškarci jesu, evo, moj muži kuhaj,

1546
01:41:39,479 --> 01:41:41,840
[SPEAKER_01] pere redovno svaku večer je suđe njegovo,

1547
01:41:41,840 --> 01:41:43,079
[SPEAKER_01] znači, ja ne brinem o tome.

1548
01:41:43,079 --> 01:41:45,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, da, odrađujete neke stvari koje prije muški nisu.

1549
01:41:46,039 --> 01:41:48,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ali generalno, mama, mama, mama,

1550
01:41:48,140 --> 01:41:50,220
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim, kako je u vrtiću bilo,

1551
01:41:50,220 --> 01:41:52,840
[SPEAKER_01] je li taj sastrak, vas, najčešće to boli briga.

1552
01:41:52,840 --> 01:41:56,640
[SPEAKER_01] I, ono, ja razmišljam je li mala roba.

1553
01:41:56,640 --> 01:41:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ne znam da li neki muškarci razmišljaju,

1554
01:41:59,199 --> 01:42:00,720
[SPEAKER_01] da li su prerasli djeca robu,

1555
01:42:00,720 --> 01:42:01,739
[SPEAKER_01] opet nek se jave.

1556
01:42:01,739 --> 01:42:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, znači, ja sve radim ko moj suprug,

1557
01:42:04,960 --> 01:42:06,899
[SPEAKER_01] znači, zarađujem, znači, sve.

1558
01:42:06,899 --> 01:42:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] I još sve ono možda što njega ne traže.

1559
01:42:10,800 --> 01:42:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] On nije doio, nije se budio.

1560
01:42:12,720 --> 01:42:14,319
[SPEAKER_01] Znači...

1561
01:42:14,319 --> 01:42:17,180
[SPEAKER_00] Čini mi se da vam je feminizm samo otežao život još više.

1562
01:42:17,180 --> 01:42:19,560
[SPEAKER_01] U jednu ruku neke stvari je u lakšu, naravno,

1563
01:42:19,560 --> 01:42:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali to samo želim reći da ne bi ju htjela odgojiti.

1564
01:42:22,159 --> 01:42:24,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ti sve možeš sama, ti sve moraš sama.

1565
01:42:24,300 --> 01:42:26,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, ljubica, budi ti ženstvena moja,

1566
01:42:26,739 --> 01:42:29,579
[SPEAKER_01] molim te, znaj prihvatiti pomoć,

1567
01:42:29,579 --> 01:42:31,220
[SPEAKER_01] znaj tražiti.

1568
01:42:31,220 --> 01:42:33,300
[SPEAKER_01] Što više radim na sebi, psihoterapijski,

1569
01:42:33,300 --> 01:42:35,619
[SPEAKER_01] to više dođem svog mužu, želim da me zbrineš.

1570
01:42:35,619 --> 01:42:38,119
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, taj osjećaj, taj dio,

1571
01:42:38,119 --> 01:42:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] da, ja mogu, ja mogu uzrežavati obitelj.

1572
01:42:40,859 --> 01:42:43,739
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja mogu, radim to, ali, znaš šta,

1573
01:42:43,739 --> 01:42:46,979
[SPEAKER_01] želim taj dio ženstvenosti.

1574
01:42:46,979 --> 01:42:48,680
[SPEAKER_01] I to želim odgojiti svojih čer,

1575
01:42:48,680 --> 01:42:49,819
[SPEAKER_01] ne da ona sve može.

1576
01:42:49,819 --> 01:42:51,439
[SPEAKER_01] To je opet i dio traume.

1577
01:42:51,439 --> 01:42:53,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sve mogu i moram sama.

1578
01:42:53,840 --> 01:42:55,300
[SPEAKER_01] To je dio opet traume.

1579
01:42:55,300 --> 01:42:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, tu je ta razlika.

1580
01:42:57,539 --> 01:43:00,260
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ipak bi ja tu svoju divojčicu odgojila,

1581
01:43:00,260 --> 01:43:02,699
[SPEAKER_01] budi i ranjiva, budi i nježna,

1582
01:43:02,699 --> 01:43:05,680
[SPEAKER_01] prihvati pomoć, ne moraš sve sama

1583
01:43:05,680 --> 01:43:06,800
[SPEAKER_01] i nećeš sve sama.

1584
01:43:06,800 --> 01:43:08,560
[SPEAKER_01] A dječak i opet možda bi,

1585
01:43:08,560 --> 01:43:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] sad možda ćemo imat hejtere tu u komentara,

1586
01:43:11,380 --> 01:43:12,140
[SPEAKER_01] ali u smislu,

1587
01:43:12,140 --> 01:43:14,279
[SPEAKER_01] taj dio

1588
01:43:14,279 --> 01:43:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] nosi.

1589
01:43:17,079 --> 01:43:19,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, budi u autoritetu.

1590
01:43:23,039 --> 01:43:24,239
[SPEAKER_01] moži sam htjela reći.

1591
01:43:24,239 --> 01:43:25,880
[SPEAKER_01] Kao, daj da možeš.

1592
01:43:25,880 --> 01:43:28,020
[SPEAKER_01] Daj tu sigurnost.

1593
01:43:28,020 --> 01:43:29,199
[SPEAKER_01] Kada ti žena rodi,

1594
01:43:29,199 --> 01:43:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] trebajo i gnjezdo.

1595
01:43:33,000 --> 01:43:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] Trebajo i da ju njeguješ.

1596
01:43:34,920 --> 01:43:36,899
[SPEAKER_01] Trebajo i da joj priuštiš sigurnost.

1597
01:43:36,899 --> 01:43:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, gled, dogod i muškarci na rađaju nije isto.

1598
01:43:40,579 --> 01:43:42,020
[SPEAKER_01] Nije isto.

1599
01:43:42,020 --> 01:43:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] Nije izašla ta beba iz njih.

1600
01:43:44,039 --> 01:43:45,659
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu propatili to što jesu

1601
01:43:45,659 --> 01:43:48,680
[SPEAKER_01] i nije im tijelo tri sljedeće godine u kaosu.

1602
01:43:48,680 --> 01:43:50,199
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, nije isto.

1603
01:43:50,199 --> 01:43:53,020
[SPEAKER_01] I zato i uloge nisu baš isti.

1604
01:43:53,619 --> 01:43:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] Znači daj jednaka prava,

1605
01:43:55,199 --> 01:43:57,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne da nam je teže.

1606
01:43:57,159 --> 01:43:58,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ne da nam je više.

1607
01:43:58,760 --> 01:43:59,520
[SPEAKER_01] To to ne bi.

1608
01:43:59,520 --> 01:44:01,319
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, tu je ta neka razlika,

1609
01:44:01,319 --> 01:44:03,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali generalno kod mene nema boja.

1610
01:44:03,039 --> 01:44:06,640
[SPEAKER_01] Nema, znači, kuhinjica i za lina,

1611
01:44:06,640 --> 01:44:07,779
[SPEAKER_01] znači za dječaka.

1612
01:44:07,779 --> 01:44:08,579
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1613
01:44:08,579 --> 01:44:10,659
[SPEAKER_01] Jer neće on bit kuhar zbog toga.

1614
01:44:10,659 --> 01:44:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] On tu uči vrlo važne vještine za život.

1615
01:44:14,000 --> 01:44:15,220
[SPEAKER_01] Lutkica isto.

1616
01:44:15,220 --> 01:44:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] Neće on bit žena jer mu dam lutku,

1617
01:44:18,079 --> 01:44:19,500
[SPEAKER_01] nego će on naučit njegovat.

1618
01:44:19,500 --> 01:44:21,500
[SPEAKER_01] Pa će njegovat sutra svoju ženu za to.

1619
01:44:21,819 --> 01:44:23,859
[SPEAKER_01] Pa će imat empatiju razvijenu prema meni

1620
01:44:23,859 --> 01:44:24,640
[SPEAKER_01] za dvije godine,

1621
01:44:24,640 --> 01:44:25,859
[SPEAKER_01] pa će se ponašat bolje.

1622
01:44:25,859 --> 01:44:27,640
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, lutkicu mu dajem za to,

1623
01:44:27,640 --> 01:44:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] a ne jer da bude curica.

1624
01:44:29,340 --> 01:44:30,699
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, ovaj,

1625
01:44:30,699 --> 01:44:33,140
[SPEAKER_01] ne brinem se mi kad mi sin kaže

1626
01:44:33,140 --> 01:44:34,460
[SPEAKER_01] da mu nalakiram nokta,

1627
01:44:34,460 --> 01:44:35,119
[SPEAKER_01] jer vidi seko.

1628
01:44:35,399 --> 01:44:37,039
[SPEAKER_01] nalakiram, pa neće on zato bit žena.

1629
01:44:37,039 --> 01:44:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ili feminizira.

1630
01:44:40,000 --> 01:44:41,460
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ne, ono,

1631
01:44:41,460 --> 01:44:43,739
[SPEAKER_01] u tom smislu sam neutralna,

1632
01:44:43,739 --> 01:44:44,659
[SPEAKER_01] puštam djete.

1633
01:44:44,659 --> 01:44:46,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ako treba biti feminiziran,

1634
01:44:46,380 --> 01:44:48,399
[SPEAKER_01] to vjerojatno će genetski doć.

1635
01:44:48,399 --> 01:44:51,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, ono, kažem,

1636
01:44:51,159 --> 01:44:52,279
[SPEAKER_01] neutralno,

1637
01:44:52,279 --> 01:44:53,699
[SPEAKER_01] nema odvojenih igračaka,

1638
01:44:53,699 --> 01:44:54,899
[SPEAKER_01] nema odvojenih boja.

1639
01:44:54,899 --> 01:44:56,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam djevojčici kupila plavi romobil.

1640
01:44:56,880 --> 01:44:58,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to još čak namjerno radim,

1641
01:44:58,140 --> 01:44:59,439
[SPEAKER_01] jer želim ljudima dokazati,

1642
01:44:59,520 --> 01:45:00,880
[SPEAKER_01] hej, nemojte, ono,

1643
01:45:00,880 --> 01:45:02,239
[SPEAKER_01] nemoj plakat jer si dečko.

1644
01:45:02,239 --> 01:45:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ne postito emocije su tu

1645
01:45:04,079 --> 01:45:05,720
[SPEAKER_01] da nas drže zdravima.

1646
01:45:05,720 --> 01:45:06,979
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, emocije su tu

1647
01:45:06,979 --> 01:45:08,119
[SPEAKER_01] da nešto otpustimo.

1648
01:45:08,119 --> 01:45:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ljutnja je tu da se izborimo.

1649
01:45:09,840 --> 01:45:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] Tuga je tu da otpustimo bol.

1650
01:45:11,500 --> 01:45:13,319
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, sve ima smisla.

1651
01:45:13,319 --> 01:45:14,760
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, ovaj,

1652
01:45:14,760 --> 01:45:17,159
[SPEAKER_01] jednak u emocijama,

1653
01:45:17,159 --> 01:45:18,439
[SPEAKER_01] jednak u igračkama,

1654
01:45:18,439 --> 01:45:19,600
[SPEAKER_01] jednak u bojama,

1655
01:45:19,600 --> 01:45:21,399
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo ti neki subtilni,

1656
01:45:21,399 --> 01:45:23,779
[SPEAKER_01] možda biološke razlike jesu tu,

1657
01:45:23,779 --> 01:45:26,239
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda i tome prilagođavamo odgoje.

1658
01:45:26,239 --> 01:45:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo sljedeći put naprijed,

1659
01:45:28,079 --> 01:45:29,600
[SPEAKER_00] odgled samo na ovu temu.

1660
01:45:29,600 --> 01:45:31,800
[SPEAKER_01] Nećemo, nećemo.

1661
01:45:31,800 --> 01:45:33,560
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo čekaj da proučim tu temu.

1662
01:45:33,560 --> 01:45:34,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ne veme o temama koje baš...

1663
01:45:34,760 --> 01:45:36,840
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo, sad ćeš proučiti ovaj,

1664
01:45:36,840 --> 01:45:37,319
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćemo,

1665
01:45:37,319 --> 01:45:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] nadam se, ljudima podijeliti nešto,

1666
01:45:40,119 --> 01:45:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] nešto zanimljivo i korist.

1667
01:45:42,159 --> 01:45:43,199
[SPEAKER_01] Što biš ti još tu?

1668
01:45:43,199 --> 01:45:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa.

1669
01:45:44,000 --> 01:45:45,260
[SPEAKER_00] Za sada je dovoljno.

1670
01:45:45,260 --> 01:45:45,939
[SPEAKER_00] Jel' dovoljno?

1671
01:45:45,939 --> 01:45:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] Za sada je dovoljno.

1672
01:45:46,420 --> 01:45:47,340
[SPEAKER_00] Mi da ćemo ljudi, jel' dovoljno?

1673
01:45:47,340 --> 01:45:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je jako atraktivna tema

1674
01:45:49,579 --> 01:45:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] i da je jako bitna.

1675
01:45:50,539 --> 01:45:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] Zahvaljujem ti se.

1676
01:45:53,239 --> 01:45:54,939
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto u tebi ukida ta tema?

1677
01:45:55,239 --> 01:45:57,600
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, možda, možda.

1678
01:45:57,600 --> 01:45:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ima neko koji ti je značajan?

1679
01:45:59,119 --> 01:46:07,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sebi zapravo mislim da dobro znam osjetiti bilo društva.

1680
01:46:08,100 --> 01:46:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, i osjećam da je ova tema sad...

1681
01:46:11,420 --> 01:46:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ok.

1682
01:46:11,739 --> 01:46:13,560
[SPEAKER_01] Definitivno.

1683
01:46:13,560 --> 01:46:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam ta koja je manje.

1684
01:46:14,960 --> 01:46:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1685
01:46:16,000 --> 01:46:16,880
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što ti je Damian rekao,

1686
01:46:16,880 --> 01:46:18,859
[SPEAKER_01] ne gledam toliko televiziju i vijesti,

1687
01:46:18,859 --> 01:46:19,939
[SPEAKER_01] baš sam nekako izolirana,

1688
01:46:19,939 --> 01:46:22,020
[SPEAKER_01] ali vjerujem, zbog moje uloge trenutno,

1689
01:46:22,020 --> 01:46:24,640
[SPEAKER_01] mama, educiram se i radim i to je puno,

1690
01:46:24,640 --> 01:46:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] ali da, to je baš, razumijem zašto to govoriš.

1691
01:46:29,180 --> 01:46:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti na još jednom gostovanju.

1692
01:46:31,539 --> 01:46:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] Uživo se.

1693
01:46:32,460 --> 01:46:33,460
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala tebi.

1694
01:46:33,460 --> 01:46:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam uživala, baš mi je bilo lijepom.

1695
01:46:35,000 --> 01:46:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala ti.

1696
01:46:35,539 --> 01:46:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi, vidimo se za tjedan dana.

1697
01:46:38,539 --> 01:46:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] Čak možda i prije.

1698
01:46:39,760 --> 01:46:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] Bok.

